high_descs: Move to the counter that is to the left of the fridge.
Pick up the plate that is on the counter.
Go to the sink with the plate.
Place the plate in the sink.  Turn the water on to wash the plate.  Pick up the plate.
Turn around with the plate go to the fridge.
Open the fridge door.  Put the plate on the top shelf.  Shut the fridge door.
anns.task_desc: Wash the plate to put in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left, walk to the counter by the refrigerator
Grab the dirty plate on the counter
Turn left, walk to the sink
Put the plate in the sink, turn on faucet, wash the plate, turn off faucet, take the clean plate
Turn around, walk back to the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator, put the plate in on the first shelf on the right
anns.task_desc: Wash the dirty plate on the counter, put it in the refrigerator

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the far right side of the kitchen counter by the fridge
Pick up the dirty plate from the kitchen counter
Turn left and walk to the kitchen sink
Wash the plate in the sink under the water and remove it
Turn right and walk back to the fridge
Put the plate into the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put the cleaned plate in the fridge
